article_text: In my interview to @thetimes I said it’s very important to push back Putin in Ukraine otherwise he will just continue. When we look at Crimea, Donbas, Georgia - every time after there was some kind of peace the next aggression has been worse than the last. thetimes.co.uk/article/if-a-…
